   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>(Recto);;Heroides to Zenon greeting. If you will kindly order the pig, about which I have several times written to you and several times spoken to you in person, to be given to Antiochos, you will do me a service. Farewell. Year 7, Pachons 15.;;(Verso);;To Zenon.</ab>
